{"tid":1543290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲綠黨正催促總理Morrison推出類似30年前8964事件的難民簽證予現持各臨時簽證逗留澳洲的香港人","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:46:32.000Z","uid":139698,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d7be8df1db428b58c3f4da50e88c61230b3668b9","tid":1543290,"uid":139698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:39:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://richard-di-natale.greensmps.org.au/articles/greens-statement-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frichard-di-natale.greensmps.org.au%2Farticles%2Fgreens-statement-hong-kong&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=73d73fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://richard-di-natale.greensmps.org.au/articles/greens-statement-hong-kong</a> <br />\n<br />\n相信身處於海外的港人係整件事上同樣面對嚴峻考驗，當我們站在香港人的立場上面對內地留學生及受黨媒薰陶下的海外華人的無理取鬧。<br />\n<br />\n甚至處於對立的局面雙方在資訊接收不同等的無奈下，我們更應心連心並堅守著相同價值觀。深受影響的不少香港留學生甚至因為其言論因為追求自由及公義，多次受到小粉紅的起底追擊甚至恐嚇要秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n當中其資料被發佈在內地的社交媒體並威脅到人生安全，在此籠罩著各種白色恐怖。面對這狀況每一位同路人更加要團結及爭取支持自由民主的政黨派系的支持及幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n唔該簽一簽，阻你一分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%3Av12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889993192&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fprime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia%3Futm_content%3Dbandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%253Av12%26recruited_by_id%3Df7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612%26recruiter%3D889993192%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dshare_petition&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=97374bd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%3Av12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889993192&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition</a><br />\n<br />\n綠黨開緊個鎖，現需要我們推開<br />\n<a href=\"https://greensmps.org.au/articles/grant-permanent-protection-all-hong-kongers-residing-australia?utm_source=miragenews&amp;utm_medium=miragenews&amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;fbclid=IwAR3dtNLdtlkseyKROBD8979Ew182E-d6ZdmZUKRlHfmauAqbFXzGUjU8sUg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreensmps.org.au%2Farticles%2Fgrant-permanent-protection-all-hong-kongers-residing-australia%3Futm_source%3Dmiragenews%26utm_medium%3Dmiragenews%26utm_campaign%3Dnews%26fbclid%3DIwAR3dtNLdtlkseyKROBD8979Ew182E-d6ZdmZUKRlHfmauAqbFXzGUjU8sUg&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=772747b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://greensmps.org.au/articles/grant-permanent-protection-all-hong-kongers-residing-australia?utm_source=miragenews&amp;utm_medium=miragenews&amp;utm_campaign=news&amp;fbclid=IwAR3dtNLdtlkseyKROBD8979Ew182E-d6ZdmZUKRlHfmauAqbFXzGUjU8sUg</a>"},{"pid":"2b19f0bbfa29e8386e6ac32ad4dab473af75987c","tid":1543290,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz